# Title: Arbitrary File Download Via IMEWDBLD.EXE
# Author: Swachchhanda Shrawan Poudel
# Date: 2023-11-09
# Level: high
# Description: Detects usage of "IMEWDBLD.exe" to download arbitrary files
# MITRE Tactic: Defense Evasion
# Tags: attack.defense-evasion, attack.execution, attack.t1218
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_imewbdld_download.yml

CommandLine IN ("*http://*", "*https://*") Image="*\\IMEWDBLD.exe" OR OriginalFileName="imewdbld.exe"